Package dk.anaha.easykv.client

Class EasyKVJava

java.lang.Object
dk.anaha.easykv.client.EasyKVJava
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.AutoCloseable
public class EasyKVJava
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.AutoCloseable
EasyKVJava is a EasyKeyValue client which method names that resemble pure Java. Should you be familiar with products like Redis then have a look at EasyKVR.java or Apache ZooKeeper then have a look at EasyKVZK.java.

However if you are are not familiar with that product then stay here this should provide easier adoption. 

 try (EasyKVJava kvs = new EasyKVJava(tcpPort)){
     kvs.connect();
     // ... your code
 }

Author:
Azri Rosborg
